title: Run-time Error "Got an unexpected keyword argument 'rate' "
body:
Please give some advice to experts.
When I run it, I get the error message` Got an unexpected keyword argument'rate'` and it doesn't work.
Even if I check the'rate', I don't know what is causing it to not work.

Running environment:
macOS Monterey (12.0.1, Intel)
Python 3.8.8
Tensorflow 2.7.0
OpenCV 4.5.4
